<h1><strong>Activation</strong></h1>
<p>1. activate <span style="color:#f1c40f">cheats</span> in the world</p>
<p><img src="https://r2.mcpedl.com/submissions/231571/images/banhammer_3.png" width="713" height="53"></p>
<p>2. activate the addon in the world</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1268676/description_eda504cb-a499-47b8-b240-3bff7a206529.png" width="711" height="153"></p>
<p>3. You are now ready and can now go into the world</p>
<p><span style="color:#f1c40f">The add-on does not require beta APIs</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><strong>id ban</strong></h1>
<p>If a player gets banned, there's the option to log into another account and unban themselves that way. The new ID ban feature is now available for this purpose. If the add-on detects that the same ID on the ban list is trying to join, the name will automatically be banned via the main account. This doesn't apply to admins.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><strong>commands</strong></h1>
<p><span style="color:#f1c40f">/ban&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;name&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;reason&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;sec&gt; &lt;min&gt; &lt;hours&gt; &lt;days&gt;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight:400">The player will be banned for 1 second, 2 minutes, 3 hours, and 4 days. If no time is specified, or if 0 seconds, 0 minutes, 0 hours, and 0 days are entered, the player will be permanently banned.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1268676/description_62e388b6-d45e-4552-9ee1-5d518838bb4b.png" width="507" height="40"></p>
<p><span style="color:#f1c40f">/pardon &lt;name&gt;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight:400">Upon execution, the player is automatically pardoned and can rejoin</span></p>
<p><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1268676/description_2719eac3-e2fa-438e-98ba-d7e28df8df61.png" width="499" height="40"></p>
<p><span style="color:#f1c40f">/c-kick &lt;name&gt; &lt;reason&gt;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight:400">The command kicks a player from the server</span></p>
<p><span style="color:#f1c40f"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1268676/description_24c7734b-e6af-4d4e-a02e-ea9847b72ce2.png" width="503" height="41"><img></span></p>
<p><span style="color:#f1c40f">/id &lt;name&gt;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight:400">displays the ID of a player</span></p>
<p><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1268676/description_37044967-2b9f-4fb3-b6de-c335f7731a92.png" width="503" height="41"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
