<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><strong>banhammer</strong></h1>
<p>If you hit an entity with the banhammer, it will be deleted—no drops, no kills, just deleted. However, if you hit a player with it, they will be banned for 24 hours by default. You can adjust the ban reason and duration by right-clicking.</p>
<p><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1268676/description_c8c08416-de2e-446e-ba59-5c251190e27a.png" width="500" height="364"></p>
